title: Denim Maxi Skirt
description: Look on-trend with minimum effort in this versatile denim skirt. It's cut to a stylish maxi length from pure cotton with a hint of stretch for comfortable wear. The panelled design lends it a voluminous feel while ensuring a flattering silhouette. It fastens with a side zip for a practical finish. M&S Collection: easy-to-wear wardrobe staples that combine classic and contemporary styles.
